  <title>3.4.1 Spindle Taper Cleaning</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">主轴锥面清洁</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">主轴锥面清洁功能可在换刀时供应空气，防止切屑和冷却液附着在主轴锥面上。(参照<link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="false" type="topiclink" href="" target="_blank" style="color:#0000ff;">注）</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><image src="Spindle Taper Cleaning_Flowchart.jpg" scale="30.00%" width="484" height="319" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Notes" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">-注-</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Notes" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">手动操作刀具夹紧/松开时不供应空气。</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:10px;"><image src="Spindle Taper Cleaning_NEW_edited.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="15.00%" width="463" height="387" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
